import { Grid, Typography } from '@mui/material' import { Box, Container } from '@mui/system' import React from 'react' import HolderImage from '../holder.jpg' const OurStory = () => { return ( the work of a lifetime As an 8 year old boy I would spend my afternoons exploring a small creek near our cabin in Northern Wisconsin. I would walk under the canopy of oak trees exploring, seeking, learning and playing on the creek's banks. When I founded Stone Creek Coffee as a 24 year old it was that ethos that I wanted to infuse into our new company. We continue this work today and welcome you to our coffee family. - Ted, Founder where we've been our history Founded by Eric Resch in 1993, Stone Creek Coffee was built on the idea that we have an obligation to care for those around us. We have endeavored to conduct our business with this authentic care as we've grown from a single, small cafe in Whitefish Bay to where we are today. We call downtown Milwaukee “home,” and we work to see the flourishing of this great city.


) } export default OurStory
